window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Set in the world of Joe Sugg’s bestselling Username comic books, Audible Originals presents Username Resurgent. Sixteen year old Serena Hall’s big brother Silas walked into the woods on his twentieth birthday and never came back. When local police call off the search, Serena takes it on herself to investigate. Starting her own true-crime podcast, she delves into a world she never knew her brother inhabited, one of supernatural urban legends and global internet mythology that seems to centre on a malevolent digital entity known as The Angel of E.Scape...</p> <p>Starring India Amarteifio, Sean Delaney, Joe Sugg, Ruth Wilson, Kit Young and a full ensemble cast featuring Abbie Andrews, Rachel Atkins, Harriet Carmichael, Saffron Coomber, Clare Corbett, Genevieve Gaunt, Julie Graham, Savannah Skinner Henry, Yasmin Mwanza, Harry Myers, Nigel Pilkington, , Richard Reed, Rish Shah, Dan Starkey, Homer Todiwala, Hannah Van Der Westhuysen and Keith Wickham</p> <p>Username: Resurgent features an original score by Hannah Peel and was Executive Produced by Joe Sugg for Final Straw Productions, Created by Joe Sugg and written by Joe Sugg and Paul Neafcy</p> <p><i>Now available in Dolby Atmos on Audible</i></p>"; 
